              <a href="Tooltip.html" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg> Tooltip</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="references" class="doc-section-title">References</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens and resources for implementing the Right Pane component.</p>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li><strong>Figma Node:</strong> <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">16359:74562</code> &mdash; Right Pane (single component, not a variant set)</li>
              <li><strong>Rail width:</strong> 48 px (fixed), full viewport height</li>
